      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you mentioned R2P (Responsibility to Protect) as a reason why it was a \"success\" initially. if the end result was a complete state collapse and a massive humanitarian crisis in the region, doesn't that mean the entire premise of the intervention was fundamentally flawed from a strategic perspective?",
